# crag demo recording — tight fit, big font

Output "/Users/petre/Desktop/crag-demo.gif"

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1320
Set Height 540
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 6
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "export PATH=/tmp/ruah-bin:$PATH"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "npx @whitehatd/crag demo"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
